USING Progress.Lang.*.

BLOCK-LEVEL ON ERROR UNDO, THROW.

CLASS Card: 
  
  DEFINE PROPERTY cType AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO 
    GET. 
    PRIVATE SET.
    
  DEFINE PROPERTY cName AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO 
    GET. 
    PRIVATE SET.
    
  DEFINE PROPERTY iValue AS INTEGER NO-UNDO
    GET.
    PRIVATE SET.

  CONSTRUCTOR PUBLIC Card(INPUT ipcName AS CHARACTER, INPUT ipiValue AS INTEGER):    
    THIS-OBJECT:cName  = ipcName.
    THIS-OBJECT:iValue = ipiValue.
    
    DISPLAY THIS-OBJECT:cName.
    PAUSE.
    
    IF THIS-OBJECT:cName = "Gold" THEN
    DO:
      DISPLAY "IN THE IF" THIS-OBJECT:cName.
      THIS-OBJECT:cType = "Wild".
    END.
    ELSE 
    DO:
      THIS-OBJECT:cType = "Standard".
    END.    
  END CONSTRUCTOR.
  
  METHOD PUBLIC LOGICAL compareCardType(INPUT ipoCard AS CLASS Card):
    RETURN THIS-OBJECT:cType = ipoCard:cType.
  END METHOD.

  DESTRUCTOR PUBLIC Card():
  END DESTRUCTOR.

END CLASS.